{"title_page": "Kumbulani Banda", "text_new": "{{short description|Zimbabwean footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n'''Kumbulani Banda''' (born 21 February 1989) is a [[Association football|footballer]], who plays for [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]].\n\n==Career==\nBanda began playing football with [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]], and went on six-month loan to Dynamos in early 2010.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=The Herald|author=Chikamhi, Eddie|title=Zimbabwe/South Africa: Arubi for Trials in SA|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201007060563.html|date=6 July 2010}}</ref> The [[Defender (association football)|left back]] left in summer 2010 [[Dynamos F.C.]] and returned to [[Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League]] rival [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20100515151623/http://www.fcdynamos.com/team Team > Dynamos F.C.]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Banda, Kumbulani}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Dynamos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Zimbabwe-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n'''Kumbulani Banda''' (born 21 February 1989) is a [[Association football|footballer]], who plays for [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]].\n\n==Career==\nBanda began playing football with [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]], and went on six-month loan to Dynamos in early 2010.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=The Herald|author=Chikamhi, Eddie|title=Zimbabwe/South Africa: Arubi for Trials in SA|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201007060563.html|date=6 July 2010}}</ref> The [[Defender (association football)|left back]] left in summer 2010 [[Dynamos F.C.]] and returned to [[Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League]] rival [[Bantu Tshintsha Guluva Rovers F.C.]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20100515151623/http://www.fcdynamos.com/team Team > Dynamos F.C.]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Banda, Kumbulani}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Zimbabwean footballers]]\n[[Category:Dynamos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n\n\n{{Zimbabwe-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Zimbabwean footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Zimbabwean footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kumbulani_Banda"}
